1955;;Room in the House;;British;;Maurice Elvey;;Patrick Barr, Hubert Gregg;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Room_in_the_House;;Ageing widow Betsy Richards stays with each of her three sons in turn, to find out who she'd prefer to spend the rest of her days with. When her favorite, Hugh, leaves for America, she becomes distressed. Finally, the sons rally round and buy Betsy her own cottage in the village.